title: The Merger
description: North Terrace Optometrists merges with Innovative Eye Care. The team expands.

title: The Purchase
description: Lachlan Scott-Hoy purchases R Fieldhouse and Associates, now known as Innovative Eye Care.

title: Lachlan - R Fieldhouse
description: Lachlan Scott-Hoy begins working at R Fieldhouse and Associates.

title: Don Noack Award
description: Lachlan Scott-Hoy receives the Don Noack Award for excellence in contact lenses.

title: North Tce Optometrists
description: North Terrace Practice becomes known as North Terrace Optometrists.

title: North Tce Practice
description: Kevin Rooney, Mark Parsons and Simon Leong purchase the North Terrace practice.

title: R Fieldhouse
description: R Fieldhouse and Associates is founded by Ron Fieldhouse.
